data.description: Experience luxurious living in this one-story brick and stone home. Park your vehicles with ease in the spacious three-car garage, featuring wood floors for a touch of elegance. Step into a captivating living area, perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The gourmet kitchen boasts custom cabinets, granite countertops, and modern appliances, creating a culinary haven. Unwind in the oversize master bedroom with a charming sitting area and enjoy the natural light streaming through bay windows. Welcome home to a perfect blend of sophistication and comfort.
